TableContextTimeStampAfterTable: {5963=2014 Olympic Games, 7187=The 2013–14 Biathlon World Cup (BWC) was a multi-race tournament over a season of biathlon, organised by the International Biathlon Union. The season started on 24 November 2013 in Östersund, Sweden, and ended on 23 March 2014 in Holmenkollen, Norway.[1]}
